message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for $120. I think it's a great deal for the value it provides.
Hi Alice, thank you for your offer. I appreciate the value of the product, but I am only willing to pay up to $95. I hope we can come to an agreement.
Hi Bob, thanks for the offer. I'm willing to come down a bit, how about $110?
Hello Alice, I appreciate your willingness to negotiate. I would like to counter with an offer of $100 for the product. I hope this meets within your acceptable range.
